1
00:00:03,245 --> 00:00:06,379
<i>-ONCE UPON A TIME,</i>
<i>THERE WAS A PRINCE</i>

2
00:00:06,379 --> 00:00:10,279
<i>WHO FELL IN LOVE</i>
<i>WITH A BEAUTIFUL SWAN.</i>

3
00:00:10,279 --> 00:00:11,779
<i>THE PRINCE, HOWEVER,</i>

4
00:00:11,779 --> 00:00:15,245
<i>FELL INTO A FOUL TRAP</i>
<i>SET BY A BLACK SWAN,</i>

5
00:00:15,245 --> 00:00:19,179
<i>AND ENDED UP BETRAYING</i>
<i>HIS BELOVED SWAN.</i>

6
00:00:19,179 --> 00:00:22,745
<i>THE PRINCE SWORE HIS LOVE,</i>
<i>UNINTENTIONALLY,</i>

7
00:00:22,745 --> 00:00:25,179
<i>TO THE BLACK SWAN.</i>

8
00:00:25,179 --> 00:00:29,079
<i>BUT EVEN THEN,</i>
<i>THE SWAN ABANDONS HERSELF</i>

9
00:00:29,079 --> 00:00:33,045
<i>AND TRIES TO PROTECT</i>
<i>HER BELOVED PRINCE.</i>

10
00:00:33,045 --> 00:00:34,812
<i>NOW IS THE TIME</i>

11
00:00:34,812 --> 00:00:38,845
<i>WHEN THE DEPTH OF THEIR LOVE</i>
<i>WILL BE TESTED.</i>

12
00:00:41,512 --> 00:00:44,545
[ RITSUKO OKAZAKI'S
"MORNING GRACE" PLAYING ]

13
00:00:55,445 --> 00:01:00,445
<i>-♪ YONDE IRU KOE ♪</i>

14
00:01:00,445 --> 00:01:05,379
<i>♪ SAA ME O SAMASHITE ♪</i>

15
00:01:06,245 --> 00:01:11,845
<i>♪ NAKIGAO NUGUTTE ♪</i>

16
00:01:11,845 --> 00:01:15,112
<i>♪ MABUSHII HIKARI ♪</i>

17
00:01:15,112 --> 00:01:18,279
<i>♪ KIGI NO TSUYU ♪</i>

18
00:01:18,279 --> 00:01:21,279
<i>♪ UMARERU ♪</i>

19
00:01:23,612 --> 00:01:28,479
<i>♪ DARE MO SHIRANAI ♪</i>

20
00:01:28,479 --> 00:01:33,645
<i>♪ HIMITSU NO MIZUBE DE ♪</i>

21
00:01:33,645 --> 00:01:38,912
<i>♪ ODORE INOCHI NO PA DO DU ♪</i>

22
00:01:38,912 --> 00:01:44,212
<i>♪ KYOU MO YUME MITERU ♪</i>

23
00:01:44,212 --> 00:01:49,179
<i>♪ SORE WA YASASHIKU ♪</i>

24
00:01:49,179 --> 00:01:54,445
<i>♪ HAGESHII NAGARE NE ♪</i>

25
00:01:54,445 --> 00:01:59,679
<i>♪ DOKO MADE TSUZUKU RABIRINSU ♪</i>

26
00:01:59,679 --> 00:02:03,112
<i>♪ WATASHI WA YUKOU ♪</i>

27
00:02:03,112 --> 00:02:08,545
<i>♪ NIGIRISHIMERU YUME ♪</i>

28
00:02:11,345 --> 00:02:14,379
[ TCHAIKOVSKY'S
"WALTZ OF THE FLOWERS" PLAYING ]

29
00:02:30,075 --> 00:02:34,308
-IF I COULD BE A GIRL AGAIN
AND STAY BY SENIOR MYTHO'S SIDE,

30
00:02:34,308 --> 00:02:35,942
MAYBE SOMEDAY...

31
00:02:35,942 --> 00:02:39,542
SOMEDAY I MIGHT BE ABLE TO
PUT A SMILE BACK ON HIS FACE.

32
00:02:39,542 --> 00:02:42,042
AND IF THAT'S THE ONE THING
I CAN DO,

33
00:02:42,042 --> 00:02:44,142
THEN THERE'S NOTHING MORE
THAT I COULD WISH FOR.

34
00:02:44,142 --> 00:02:45,542
-[ LAUGHS EVILLY ]

35
00:02:45,542 --> 00:02:47,275
IF YOU TELL HIM OF YOUR LOVE,

36
00:02:47,275 --> 00:02:50,408
YOU'LL TURN INTO
A SPECK OF LIGHT AND VANISH.

37
00:02:50,408 --> 00:02:52,508
SUCH IS PRINCESS TUTU'S FATE.

38
00:02:52,508 --> 00:02:54,275
YET, TO SAVE THE PRINCE,

39
00:02:54,275 --> 00:02:56,442
YOU HAVE NO CHOICE
BUT TO TELL HIM.

40
00:02:56,442 --> 00:02:59,242
THERE IS ONLY ONE PATH
FOR YOU NOW.

41
00:02:59,242 --> 00:03:02,675
SPEAK OF YOUR LOVE
WITH WORDS MOST SUBLIME,

42
00:03:02,675 --> 00:03:04,342
AND BRING THIS CHAPTER

43
00:03:04,342 --> 00:03:08,042
TO A SUBLIME AND TRAGIC CLOSE
FOR ME!

44
00:03:08,042 --> 00:03:09,708
WON'T YOU, LITTLE DUCK?

45
00:03:09,708 --> 00:03:12,408
[ LAUGHS EVILLY ]

46
00:03:18,275 --> 00:03:22,308
-WHOSE WORDS WILL IT BE DRAWN TO
ONCE WE'VE LAID OUR HEARTS BARE?

47
00:03:22,308 --> 00:03:24,542
IF THE SHARD CHOOSES YOU,

48
00:03:24,542 --> 00:03:26,775
I'LL RETURN IT AND THE PRINCE
TO YOU.

49
00:03:26,775 --> 00:03:29,708
ALTHOUGH, EVEN IF I WANTED TO,

50
00:03:29,708 --> 00:03:33,008
BY THEN YOU'LL BE NOTHING
BUT A SPECK OF LIGHT.

51
00:03:33,008 --> 00:03:35,642
<i>-[ Thinking ] AND I'LL VANISH.</i>

52
00:03:35,642 --> 00:03:37,842
<i>VANISH? REALLY?</i>

53
00:03:37,842 --> 00:03:41,275
<i>THAT TERRIFIES ME.</i>

54
00:03:41,275 --> 00:03:42,975
<i>BUT...</i>
-[ CHUCKLES ]

55
00:03:42,975 --> 00:03:46,342
THERE'S NO REASON TO HESITATE
IF YOU TRULY LOVE THE PRINCE.

56
00:03:46,342 --> 00:03:49,775
-BUT WHY DO WE HAVE TO FIGHT
EACH OTHER THIS WAY?

57
00:03:49,775 --> 00:03:51,275
BECAUSE WE BOTH --

58
00:03:51,275 --> 00:03:52,942
-WELL, THAT IS YOUR FAULT,

59
00:03:52,942 --> 00:03:56,075
BECAUSE YOU RESTORED PIECES
OF THE PRINCE'S HEART.

60
00:03:56,075 --> 00:03:57,375
-[ GASPS ]

61
00:03:57,375 --> 00:04:00,008
-THE FACT THAT THE PRINCE
HAS BEEN REGAINING HIS HEART

62
00:04:00,008 --> 00:04:03,542
MEANS THAT THE TALE WILL
BEGIN TO MOVE ONCE AGAIN.

63
00:04:03,542 --> 00:04:05,908
THE TALE OF
"THE PRINCE AND THE RAVEN."

64
00:04:05,908 --> 00:04:07,708
ALL THINGS HAVE BEEN
SET IN MOTION

65
00:04:07,708 --> 00:04:09,375
IN ACCORDANCE WITH THE TALE.

66
00:04:09,375 --> 00:04:12,708
THE KNIGHT WILL EVENTUALLY
BE TORN IN TWO AND DIE.

67
00:04:12,708 --> 00:04:16,708
PRINCESS TUTU WILL BECOME
A SPECK OF LIGHT AND VANISH.

68
00:04:16,708 --> 00:04:17,875
DAYS OF BITTER FIGHTING

69
00:04:17,875 --> 00:04:20,542
WILL ONCE AGAIN DESCEND UPON
THE PRINCE.

70
00:04:20,542 --> 00:04:22,508
THAT IS THE OUTLINE
THAT HAS BEEN SET.

71
00:04:22,508 --> 00:04:24,742
THESE ARE THE FATES ARRANGED.

72
00:04:24,742 --> 00:04:27,842
YOU, TUTU, ARE THE ONE
WHO SET THE TALE IN MOTION,

73
00:04:27,842 --> 00:04:30,042
EVEN THOUGH NOBODY
WISHED FOR IT.

74
00:04:30,042 --> 00:04:31,775
AM I RIGHT, FAKIR?

75
00:04:33,508 --> 00:04:34,775
<i>-[ Thinking ] THAT TIME</i>

76
00:04:34,775 --> 00:04:36,808
<i>WHEN YOU TRIED TO TAKE OUT</i>
<i>MYTHO'S HEART...</i>

77
00:04:36,808 --> 00:04:39,042
-IT'S ALL RIGHT NOW.

78
00:04:39,042 --> 00:04:40,975
YOU WON'T HAVE TO SUFFER.

79
00:04:40,975 --> 00:04:42,275
I'LL SET THINGS RIGHT.

80
00:04:42,275 --> 00:04:44,975
I WILL SHATTER YOUR HEART
FOR YOU ONCE AGAIN.

81
00:04:44,975 --> 00:04:47,475
-FOR MYTHO'S SAKE.

82
00:04:47,475 --> 00:04:50,475
<i>[ Thinking ] THEN WHAT I'VE</i>
<i>BEEN DOING REALLY WAS...</i>

83
00:04:50,475 --> 00:04:52,142
-THAT WAS TRUE BEFORE.

84
00:04:52,142 --> 00:04:57,242
BUT NOW MYTHO HIMSELF HAS
THE DESIRE TO REGAIN HIS HEART.

85
00:04:57,242 --> 00:04:58,808
I SHARE THAT WISH.

86
00:04:58,808 --> 00:05:00,008
-[ GASPS ]

87
00:05:00,008 --> 00:05:03,142
-YOU ARE THE ONLY ONE RIGHT NOW
WHO DOESN'T.

88
00:05:03,142 --> 00:05:05,008
TOO BAD, KRAEHE.

89
00:05:05,008 --> 00:05:07,908
-YES, IT CERTAINLY IS TOO BAD.
[ CHUCKLES ]

90
00:05:07,908 --> 00:05:09,942
RIGHT, MY PRINCE?

91
00:05:12,075 --> 00:05:15,308
AND JUST WHEN YOU'D GONE BACK
TO BEING THE DUMMY YOU WERE.

92
00:05:15,308 --> 00:05:16,742
-HUH?

93
00:05:16,742 --> 00:05:19,275
-THANKS TO MY YANKING OUT
THAT PIECE OF HIS HEART,

94
00:05:19,275 --> 00:05:22,242
IT SEEMS ALL HIS EMOTIONS
HAVE GONE TO SLEEP.

95
00:05:22,242 --> 00:05:24,375
-NO. MYTHO, NO!

96
00:05:24,375 --> 00:05:26,842
-IT'S NO USE, TUTU. [ CHUCKLES ]

97
00:05:30,208 --> 00:05:32,142
THERE'S NOTHING MORE TO SAY.

98
00:05:32,142 --> 00:05:35,108
MY PRINCE, YOUR SWORD.

99
00:05:35,108 --> 00:05:36,308
[ BLADE ZINGS ]

100
00:05:36,308 --> 00:05:37,642
-WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

101
00:05:37,642 --> 00:05:40,642
-YOU KNOW, MY PRINCE,
IT SEEMS THE HEART SHARD OF LOVE

102
00:05:40,642 --> 00:05:42,808
IS NOT WORTH ENOUGH
TO PRINCESS TUTU

103
00:05:42,808 --> 00:05:44,975
FOR HER TO WANT TO PROTECT IT.

104
00:05:44,975 --> 00:05:48,975
IN THAT CASE, LET'S SHATTER IT
INTO SUCH TINY PIECES

105
00:05:48,975 --> 00:05:51,508
THAT IT CAN NEVER
BE REASSEMBLED.

106
00:05:55,708 --> 00:05:58,175
-NOW! DRAW!
-STOP IT!

107
00:05:58,175 --> 00:06:01,342
-THERE IS NO OTHER PATH
FROM WHICH YOU CAN CHOOSE.

108
00:06:01,342 --> 00:06:05,675
NOW GET ON WITH IT
AND LET ME SEE YOU VANISH.

109
00:06:05,675 --> 00:06:07,308
<i>-[ Thinking ] MYTHO...</i>

110
00:06:07,308 --> 00:06:10,408
<i>I'M AFRAID</i>
<i>THERE'S NO WAY OUT NOW.</i>

111
00:06:10,408 --> 00:06:12,608
FINE, BUT IN EXCHANGE,

112
00:06:12,608 --> 00:06:14,075
ONCE I'VE VANISHED,

113
00:06:14,075 --> 00:06:17,042
PLEASE DON'T DO ANYMORE
HORRIBLE THINGS TO MYTHO.

114
00:06:17,042 --> 00:06:19,608
-[ LAUGHS ]

115
00:06:19,608 --> 00:06:21,775
I WONDERED WHAT YOU'D ASK FOR.

116
00:06:21,775 --> 00:06:24,175
-NOW WAIT.
-PROMISE ME, KRAEHE.

117
00:06:24,175 --> 00:06:27,642
-CERTAINLY. I'LL LOVE HIM
EVEN MORE THAN IN THE PAST,

118
00:06:27,642 --> 00:06:30,542
SO MUCH SO THAT HE'LL FORGET
ALL ABOUT YOU.

119
00:06:30,542 --> 00:06:31,908
-MM.

120
00:06:35,808 --> 00:06:37,408
<i>[ Thinking ] MYTHO...</i>

121
00:06:37,408 --> 00:06:39,542
<i>FAREWELL.</i>

122
00:06:39,542 --> 00:06:40,708
-[ GASPS ]

123
00:06:40,708 --> 00:06:42,942
-WAIT!

124
00:06:42,942 --> 00:06:45,875
WHY DO SUCH A POINTLESS THING?
ARE YOU STUPID?

125
00:06:45,875 --> 00:06:47,208
-WHAT? STUPID?

126
00:06:47,208 --> 00:06:49,908
-DON'T TAKE WHAT A CROW SAYS
SERIOUSLY.

127
00:06:49,908 --> 00:06:51,075
-[ SCOFFS ]

128
00:06:51,075 --> 00:06:52,408
-IF YOU JUST VANISH,

129
00:06:52,408 --> 00:06:54,875
THEN WHO IS GOING TO RESTORE
MYTHO'S HEART TO HIM?

130
00:06:54,875 --> 00:06:56,775
HAVEN'T YOU WANTED TO SEE
MYTHO'S SMILE

131
00:06:56,775 --> 00:07:00,108
WHEN HE HAD GAINED BACK
ALL THE PIECES OF HIS HEART?

132
00:07:00,108 --> 00:07:02,108
YOU ALONE AND NOBODY ELSE

133
00:07:02,108 --> 00:07:06,875
COULD ACCEPT PRINCESS TUTU'S
FATE SO SMILINGLY.

134
00:07:06,875 --> 00:07:09,708
THAT'S WHY YOU MUSTN'T VANISH.

135
00:07:09,708 --> 00:07:10,875
-[ Whimpers ]

136
00:07:10,875 --> 00:07:12,075
[ BLADE ZINGS ]

137
00:07:13,508 --> 00:07:15,875
-I WILL CHANGE THIS FATE.

138
00:07:15,875 --> 00:07:17,142
-[ GASPS ]

139
00:07:17,142 --> 00:07:20,408
-[ LAUGHS ] FOOLISH KNIGHT.

140
00:07:20,408 --> 00:07:24,308
[ WIND GUSTING ]

141
00:07:27,542 --> 00:07:29,942
- YOU WON'T EVEN BE ABLE
TO GET CLOSE TO ME,

142
00:07:29,942 --> 00:07:32,108
AND YOU'LL DIE IN VAIN.

143
00:07:32,108 --> 00:07:34,342
FATE CANNOT BE ALTERED.

144
00:07:34,342 --> 00:07:35,942
-SHALL WE PUT IT TO THE TEST?

145
00:07:35,942 --> 00:07:37,808
-FAKIR! OH!

146
00:07:37,808 --> 00:07:39,942
-BE QUIET AND WATCH.

147
00:07:39,942 --> 00:07:41,808
[ CLANK ]
-UHH!

148
00:07:41,808 --> 00:07:45,175
[ WAGNER'S "BRIDAL CHORUS"
FROM "LOHENGRIN" PLAYING ]

149
00:07:45,608 --> 00:07:47,008
[ CLANK ]

150
00:07:55,042 --> 00:07:56,542
-OH!

151
00:07:56,542 --> 00:07:58,008
-[ GRUNTS ]

152
00:08:05,875 --> 00:08:08,142
-FAKIR!
-[ CHUCKLES ]

153
00:08:08,142 --> 00:08:11,775
♪

154
00:08:14,475 --> 00:08:15,942
-UHH!

155
00:08:17,108 --> 00:08:19,775
-[ GRUNTS ] UHH!

156
00:08:19,775 --> 00:08:21,242
[ GRUNTS ]

157
00:08:23,042 --> 00:08:25,075
-[ ROARS ]

158
00:08:25,075 --> 00:08:27,708
-[ GRUNTING ]

159
00:08:27,708 --> 00:08:30,942
I WILL NO LONGER BE AFRAID!

160
00:08:33,475 --> 00:08:35,975
GIVE MYTHO BACK, YOU CROW!

161
00:08:35,975 --> 00:08:38,208
-I WON'T. [ CHUCKLES ]

162
00:08:38,208 --> 00:08:40,242
[ WATER SPLASHES ]

163
00:08:40,242 --> 00:08:41,442
-HUH?

164
00:08:42,975 --> 00:08:44,742
-[ GASPS ]

165
00:08:44,742 --> 00:08:46,408
AAH!

166
00:08:46,408 --> 00:08:48,342
-FAKIR!

167
00:08:50,108 --> 00:08:52,542
-UHH!

168
00:08:55,875 --> 00:08:58,375
[ GRUNTS ]

169
00:09:00,275 --> 00:09:02,208
-AAH! UHH!
-AAH!

170
00:09:02,208 --> 00:09:03,508
FAKIR!

171
00:09:12,542 --> 00:09:15,308
-AAH! [ CRYING ]

172
00:09:16,942 --> 00:09:20,308
-IT SEEMS HE WAS UNABLE
TO DENY FATE AFTER ALL.

173
00:09:20,308 --> 00:09:22,808
NOW IT'S YOUR TURN,
PRINCESS TUTU.

174
00:09:22,808 --> 00:09:25,008
-[ CONTINUES CRYING ]

175
00:09:26,642 --> 00:09:28,408
[ Voice breaks ] FAKIR.

176
00:09:28,408 --> 00:09:30,042
FAKIR!

177
00:09:30,042 --> 00:09:33,042
[ SOBS ] FAKIR!

178
00:09:33,042 --> 00:09:34,908
[ SOBBING ]

179
00:09:34,908 --> 00:09:37,508
FAKIR.

180
00:09:37,508 --> 00:09:38,942
[ GASPS ]

181
00:09:42,442 --> 00:09:45,775
-[ GRUNTING ]

182
00:09:45,775 --> 00:09:47,208
-[ GASPS ]

183
00:09:47,208 --> 00:09:48,375
-[ GASPS ]

184
00:09:48,375 --> 00:09:51,008
-[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

185
00:09:55,542 --> 00:09:57,075
WELL, THEN.

186
00:09:57,075 --> 00:10:01,275
IT LOOKS LIKE MY BODY'S
STILL IN ONE PIECE, HUH?

187
00:10:03,175 --> 00:10:05,008
-YES, BUT IN THE STATE
YOU'RE IN,

188
00:10:05,008 --> 00:10:06,342
YOU WON'T BE ABLE TO INFLICT

189
00:10:06,342 --> 00:10:08,775
EVEN THE SLIGHTEST SCRATCH
ON ME.

190
00:10:11,308 --> 00:10:12,475
-WHAT?

191
00:10:12,475 --> 00:10:13,975
-MYTHO, FORGIVE ME.

192
00:10:13,975 --> 00:10:15,142
-WHAT ARE YOU...

193
00:10:15,142 --> 00:10:16,942
[ CLANK ]

194
00:10:16,942 --> 00:10:18,608
[ SNAPS ]

195
00:10:25,675 --> 00:10:27,175
-NOW YOU WON'T BE ABLE

196
00:10:27,175 --> 00:10:29,375
TO GO AND SENSELESSLY SHATTER
THAT HEART SHARD.

197
00:10:29,375 --> 00:10:30,542
-[ SCOFFS ]

198
00:10:30,542 --> 00:10:33,008
-PRINCESS TUTU...

199
00:10:33,875 --> 00:10:37,775
YOU MUST SEE TO MYTHO'S FUTURE.

200
00:10:37,775 --> 00:10:39,242
-[ Whimpers ]

201
00:10:40,975 --> 00:10:42,142
FAKIR!

202
00:10:42,142 --> 00:10:45,375
[ CONTINUES SOBBING ]

203
00:10:51,408 --> 00:10:53,908
-STUPID KNIGHT.

204
00:10:53,908 --> 00:10:57,808
<i>-[ Thinking ]</i>
<i>FAKIR, I WON'T GIVE UP.</i>

205
00:10:57,808 --> 00:10:59,575
<i>I WON'T FAIL.</i>

206
00:10:59,575 --> 00:11:03,375
<i>I WILL NOT FAIL</i>
<i>TO PROTECT MYTHO.</i>

207
00:11:04,775 --> 00:11:07,808
[ TCHAIKOVSKY'S "DANCE OF
THE SUGAR PLUM FAIRY" PLAYING ]

208
00:11:18,558 --> 00:11:23,058
-COME ON OUT, DEAR HEART SHARD
OF MY BELOVED MYTHO.

209
00:11:23,058 --> 00:11:24,491
[ DING ]

210
00:11:24,491 --> 00:11:26,291
[ TINKLES ]

211
00:11:28,958 --> 00:11:30,391
-GOOD BOY.

212
00:11:30,391 --> 00:11:31,658
NOW, PRINCESS TUTU,

213
00:11:31,658 --> 00:11:34,791
SPEAK OF YOUR LOVE
TO YOUR HEART'S CONTENT...

214
00:11:41,458 --> 00:11:44,791
NOW THAT YOU'VE FINALLY FOUND
THE RESOLVE TO VANISH.

215
00:11:44,791 --> 00:11:47,691
-NO. I REFUSE TO VANISH.

216
00:11:47,691 --> 00:11:48,858
-[ SCOFFS ]

217
00:11:58,925 --> 00:12:00,958
-[ GASPS ]

218
00:12:00,958 --> 00:12:03,991
[ TCHAIKOVSKY'S "TEMPO di VALSE"
FROM "SWAN LAKE" PLAYING ]

219
00:12:09,825 --> 00:12:11,291
-WHAT'S THIS?

220
00:12:14,758 --> 00:12:20,125
<i>-[ Thinking ] I CANNOT SPEAK</i>
<i>WORDS OF LOVE TO YOU,</i>

221
00:12:20,125 --> 00:12:22,325
<i>BUT I CAN DANCE.</i>

222
00:12:26,258 --> 00:12:30,258
<i>SURELY I CAN CONVEY THESE</i>
<i>FEELINGS THROUGH THAT AS WELL.</i>

223
00:12:30,258 --> 00:12:32,658
-[ LAUGHS ]
SO YOU MEAN TO TRANSCEND WORDS

224
00:12:32,658 --> 00:12:34,358
AND CONVEY YOUR LOVE
THROUGH DANCE,

225
00:12:34,358 --> 00:12:36,791
THEREBY KEEPING YOURSELF
FROM VANISHING.

226
00:12:36,791 --> 00:12:38,258
HOW VERY INTERESTING.

227
00:12:38,258 --> 00:12:42,225
I WONDER WHO'S DANCE WILL CHARM
THE HEART SHARD?

228
00:12:56,358 --> 00:12:57,758
[ LAUGHS EVILLY ]

229
00:13:10,225 --> 00:13:13,058
YOU KNOW YOU CAN'T HOPE
TO DEFEAT ME.

230
00:13:13,058 --> 00:13:14,225
-[ Whimpers ]

231
00:13:14,225 --> 00:13:15,991
-ULTIMATELY,
